      <body>
			      <div type="debateSection" subtype="opening" xml:id="dbsect_0">
				
				        <p>The House met at <time when="2011-06-10T10:02:00+02:00" type="recordedTime"> 10.02 a.m.</time>
				        </p>
				
				        <note type="narrative">[MR. SPEAKER IN THE CHAIR]</note>
