			      <div type="debateSection" subtype="quorum" xml:id="dbsect_2">
				
				        <head>QUORUM
			</head>
				        <div type="debateSection" subtype="quorum" xml:id="dbsect_2__dbsect_1">
					          <u who="#epsilon">
						            <note type="speaker">
Mr. Epsilon: </note>
						            <seg>On a point of order,  Mr. Speaker, Sir. We are discussing the President's Speech. The mere fact that we do not have enough hon. Members might mean that it is not a popular Speech. There is no quorum in this House and could you ensure that there is quorum and then we can continue in order to show that themPresident's Speech is popular and he is also a popular President as well?</seg>
					          </u>
					          <u who="#speaker">
						            <note type="speaker">The  Speaker:</note>
						            <seg>Hon. Members, yes, I have checked and apparently the House lacks quorum at the moment. Ring the Division Bell.</seg>
					          </u>
					          <note type="summary">(The Division Bell was rung)</note>
					
					          <u who="#speaker">
						            <note type="speaker">The Speaker:</note>
						            <seg>
 Order, hon. Members! We have a quorum now. Please, proceed with the Division!</seg>
					          </u>
				        </div>
			      </div>
			      <div type="debateSection" subtype="division" xml:id="dbsect_3">
				
				        <head>DIVISION</head>
				        <note type="summary">(Question put and the House divided)</note>
				        <div type="debateSection" subtype="division" xml:id="dbsect_3__dbsect_1">
					          <u who="#speaker">
						            <note type="speaker">Mr. Speaker:</note>
						            <seg>Order! Order! 15 minutes are now over and those who wish to vote must be in the lobbies. If you are not wihtin the lobbies, you will not allowd to vote any more</seg>
					          </u>
					          <incident>
                  <desc>(Loud consultation)</desc>
               </incident>
					          <u who="#speaker">
						            <note type="speaker">Mr. Speaker:</note>
						            <seg>Order! Order! The Division is now over and it is time to receive the results</seg>
					          </u>
					          <note type="summary" xml:id="summary_1">(Question carried by <measure xml:id="quantity_1" corresp="#ayes" quantity="72">72</measure> to <measure xml:id="quantity_2" corresp="#noes" quantity="56"> 56</measure> votes)</note>
				        </div>
				        <div type="debateSection" subtype="AYES" xml:id="dbsect_3__dbsect_2">
